薄扶林，封而三個地方，成個南區成孤島，走都走唔到。<br />\n之前香港仔隧道巴士佬大戰的士佬，成個南區塞住咗。"},{"pid":"bb9b9ccd8cc5939615d90329af4ca2f7e40cc20f","tid":1440390,"uid":54940,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"南區離開得5條路<br />\n<br />\n一 香隧，即巴士，隔離就警校，長期塞車<br />\n<br />\n二 地鐵，可封<br />\n<br />\n三 薄扶林，山路黎，行都行死人，而且係一條斜路，一封係完全無得走第二條路<br />\n<br />\n四 山路，香港仔水塘可以行到去灣仔同山頂，都係行死人<br />\n<br />\n五 水路，去南Y島同長洲，即係廢既<br />\n<br />\n值得示威既地點<br />\n<br />\n一 警校<br />\n<br />\n二 田灣"},{"pid":"87e49ecb9591a6659543e838e757a0a278d5df87","tid":1440390,"uid":154012,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"只能說 南區不是一個好地方去搞呢d<br />\n利申 南區人"},{"pid":"4b1ba25182b162cde9fa334a070304cb747de226","tid":1440390,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"仲有係無大型商場可以入<br />\n無得避"},{"pid":"8c398577705cd77626fca0fd57c57922edf6e6d9","tid":1440390,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf5dffd89098c28fc602f855a67eb6ec67bbc0ae","tid":1440390,"uid":284264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:25:09.000Z","msg":"得一條隧道同MTR，唔係就要行山走，好麻煩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"域多利道<br />\n薄扶林道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9dce11b610e033532b4df75cbffc72d854ed21","tid":1440390,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"住南區，表示好想光復田灣，但真係唔好黎，南區其實好過離島小小炸，入咗黎出唔番去！"},{"pid":"e4fe80c4f7d1791c3e631a579775f8baa7effc30","tid":1440390,"uid":269973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"全部山頭，點走⋯（認真）"},{"pid":"e8f5464b41eceebc0a9631af491aa83f2ff065f5","tid":1440390,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"唔通海洋公園。。"},{"pid":"7c5c614589f08221d593e9e5e9df7b363dad5333","tid":1440390,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited